_:N0dee7d56636644ff9510fd0bd0deb687 <http://schema.org/description> "S4C is the only Welsh language public service broadcaster. It commissions independent producers from across Wales to make the majority of its programmes. S4C broadcasts sport, drama, music, factual, entertainment and events programmes, across a range of platforms, including online. S4C works with the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ." .
